&lt;/div>&lt;p>The package can also search for &lt;code>R&lt;/code> Markdown files, PDFs, and text (&lt;code>.txt&lt;/code>) files via the &lt;code>findRmd()&lt;/code>, &lt;code>findPDF()&lt;/code>, and &lt;code>findtxt()&lt;/code> functions, respectively. Each of the functions can also copy the files that matched the &lt;code>pattern&lt;/code> argument to a new folder (if &lt;code>copy = TRUE&lt;/code>, but it is &lt;code>FALSE&lt;/code> by default). You can decide which folder the files get copied to using the &lt;code>folder&lt;/code> argument. Note that by default &lt;code>overwrite&lt;/code> is set to &lt;code>TRUE&lt;/code>, so any files present with the same name will be overwritten.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>